You can use single line "if and else" to reduce your code line:

Format of single line if and else:
value_when_true if condition else value_when_false

for example: 

fruit = 'Apple'
isApple = True if fruit == 'Apple' else False

For more information you can visit: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2802726/putting-a-simple-if-then-else-statement-on-one-line
